%C A000567 From _Lekraj Beedassy_, Oct 02 2003: (Start)
%C A000567 Also the number of distinct three-cell blocks that may be removed out of A000217(n+1) square cells arranged in a stepping triangular array of side (n+1). A 5-layer triangular array of square cells, for instance, has vertices outlined thus:
%C A000567   x x
%C A000567   x x x
%C A000567   x x x x
%C A000567   x x x x x
